<Law Lang="ja" Era="Showa" Year="58" Num="006" PromulgateMonth="03" PromulgateDay="08" LawType="MinisterialOrdinance"><LawNum>昭和五十八年運輸省令第六号</LawNum><LawBody><LawTitle Kana="せんぱくじどうかせつびとくしゅきそく" Abbrev="" AbbrevKana="">船舶自動化設備特殊規則</LawTitle>
